Term::EditLine
==============

Term::EditLine is an object oriented perl interface to the NetBSD editline
library. To use the module you will have to install this library first. Read
the pod documentation for more information on this module.

INSTALLATION

Install libedit, for instance with this command in Ubuntu:

    sudo apt install libedit-dev
    
To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

libedit

